  "content": "<USER_REQUEST>\nI have created a predictive model about MLB that compiling probs and odds. \nI want you to keep the UI as it is but replace the mock stats with real ones. \nI want you to: \n\n- create a new project on my supabase profile\n- use my github (new project) in order to push everything to my vercel profile. \n- use real stats. if there is no links in the code use fangraphs and baseballsavant. \n- for the weather update use covers.com\n- built everything for me incl. supabase and github new project, new folder on my pc etc.\n\nthe code: \n\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"el\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>MLB Betting Intelligence v8</title>\n<style>\n:root{\n  --bg:#0f1117;--bg2:#171b26;--bg3:#1e2335;--bg4:#252b40;\n  --bdr:rgba(255,255,255,.07);--bdr2:rgba(255,255,255,.13);\n  --tx:#e8eaf0;--tx2:#8b91a8;--tx3:#555d78;\n  --g:#00d68f;--gbg:rgba(0,214,143,.1);--gbr:rgba(0,214,143,.28);\n  --y:#ffd166;--ybg:rgba(255,209,102,.1);--ybr:rgba(255,209,102,.28);\n  --r:#ef476f;--rbg:rgba(239,71,111,.1);--rbr:rgba(239,71,111,.28);\n  --b:#4da6ff;--bbg:rgba(77,166,255,.1);--bbr:rgba(77,166,255,.28);\n  --pu:#a78bfa;--pubg:rgba(167,139,250,.1);\n  --or:#ff9f43;--orbg:rgba(255,159,67,.1);\n  --R:10px;--Rs:6px;\n}\n*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}\nbody{background:var(--bg);color:var(--tx);font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}\n.app{max-width:1160px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 16px}\n.hdr{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}\n.hdr-l{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}\n.ico{width:36px;height:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4da6ff,#a78bfa);border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:19px;flex-shrink:0}\n.hdr h1{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}\n.hdr p{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2);margin-top:1px}\n.hstats{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.hs{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--Rs);padding:5px 10px;text-align:center}\n.hs .hv{font-size:14px;font-weight:700}.hs .hl{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2)}\n.tabs{display:flex;gap:3px;background:var(--bg2);padding:4px;border-radius:var(--R);margin-bottom:14px;overflow-x:auto}\n.tab{padding:6px 12px;border-radius:var(--Rs);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;color:var(--tx2);white-space:nowrap;transition:all .15s}\n.tab.active{background:var(--bg4);color:var(--tx)}\n.panel{display:none}.panel.active{display:block}\n.g5{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px}\n.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:11px;margin-bottom:12px}\n@media(max-width:760px){.g5{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.g2{grid-template-columns:1fr}}\n.mc{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--Rs);padding:10px 12px}\n.mc .lbl{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px}\n.mc .val{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin:2px 0}.mc .sub{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3)}\n.sec{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:var(--tx2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;margin:12px 0 6px}\n.card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--R);padding:12px}\n.card h3{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;color:var(--tx2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:8px}\n.tag{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--tx2);margin:1px}\n.tag.t1{background:rgba(255,215,0,.15);color:#ffd700}\n.tag.t2{background:var(--gbg);color:var(--g)}\n.tag.t3{background:var(--bbg);color:var(--b)}\n.tag.t4{background:var(--rbg);color:var(--r)}\n\n/* GAME CARD */\n.gc{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--R);margin-bottom:8px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .15s}\n.gc:hover{border-color:var(--bdr2)}.gc.open{border-color:rgba(77,166,255,.3)}\n.gc-head{padding:10px 13px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}\n.gc-head:hover{background:var(--bg3)}\n.gc-top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px}\n.mup{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;flex:1}\n.tb{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;min-width:46px}\n.ta{font-size:14px;font-weight:700}.tw{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2)}\n.str-pill{font-size:9px;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-weight:700;margin-top:1px}\n.sW{background:var(--gbg);color:var(--g)}.sL{background:var(--rbg);color:var(--r)}\n.gc-time{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2);white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}\n.weather-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:3px 0;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2);border-top:1px solid var(--bdr)}\n.w-icon{font-size:12px}\n.w-adj{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px}\n.w-up{background:var(--rbg);color:var(--r)}.w-down{background:var(--bbg);color:var(--b)}.w-neutral{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--tx2)}\n.pitcher-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:6px;padding:5px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--bdr)}\n.p-side{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;flex:1}\n.p-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:600}\n.p-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.p-stat{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2)}\n.p-vs{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);text-align:center;padding-top:4px;flex-shrink:0}\n.tier-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;flex-shrink:0}\n.t1d{background:#ffd700}.t2d{background:var(--g)}.t3d{background:var(--b)}.t4d{background:var(--r)}\n\n/* BEST BET BANNER */\n.best-bet{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:7px 13px;background:var(--bg4);border-top:1px solid var(--bdr);flex-wrap:wrap}\n.bb-label{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;white-space:nowrap}\n.bb-pick{font-size:12px;font-weight:700}\n.bb-odds{font-size:10px;color:var(--b);margin-left:4px}\n.bb-grade{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;margin-left:4px}\n.bb-ev{font-size:10px;color:var(--g);margin-left:4px}\n.bb-reason{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2);margin-left:auto}\n\n.picks{display:flex;gap:5px;padding:0 13px 10px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.pk{flex:1;min-width:88px;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--Rs);padding:6px 8px;position:relative}\n.pk.best-pick{border-color:rgba(0,214,143,.4);background:rgba(0,214,143,.04)}\n.pk .pt{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.3px}\n.pk .pv{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;margin:2px 0}\n.pk .or{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.pk .mo{font-size:11px;color:var(--b)}.pk .mkt{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2)}\n.gr{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px}\n.gS{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd700,#ff8c00);color:#000}\n.gA{background:var(--gbg);color:var(--g);border:1px solid var(--gbr)}\n.gB{background:var(--bbg);color:var(--b);border:1px solid var(--bbr)}\n.gC{background:var(--ybg);color:var(--y);border:1px solid var(--ybr)}\n.gD{background:var(--bg4);color:var(--tx2);border:1px solid var(--bdr2)}\n.pk .ev{font-size:9px;margin-top:2px}\n.best-star{position:absolute;top:4px;right:4px;font-size:9px;color:var(--g)}\n\n.gc-det{display:none;padding:0 13px 12px;border-top:1px solid var(--bdr)}\n.gc.open .gc-det{display:block}\n.dc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-top:10px}\n.dc h4{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2);margin-bottom:5px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.3px}\n.dr{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:3px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bdr);font-size:11px}\n.dr:last-child{border:none}\n.dn{color:var(--tx2)}.dv{font-weight:600}\n.dv.g{color:var(--g)}.dv.r{color:var(--r)}.dv.y{color:var(--y)}.dv.b{color:var(--b)}\n.pb{margin-top:7px}\n.pb-lbl{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2);margin-bottom:3px}\n.pb-tr{height:5px;background:var(--bg4);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}\n.pb-fl{height:100%;border-radius:3px}\n.context-box{background:var(--bg4);border-radius:var(--Rs);padding:8px 10px;margin-top:8px;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--tx2)}\n.context-box strong{color:var(--tx)}\n\n/* VALUE BETS */\n.vb{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--R);padding:10px 12px;margin-bottom:7px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.vb:hover{border-color:var(--bdr2)}\n.vb-gr{font-size:17px;font-weight:800;width:26px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:2px}\n.vb-info{flex:1;min-width:110px}\n.vb-match{font-size:12px;font-weight:700}\n.vb-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2);margin-top:2px;line-height:1.5}\n.vb-odds{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:2px;flex-shrink:0}\n.vb-model{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--b)}\n.vb-mkt{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2)}\n.vb-edge{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--g)}\n.vb-ev{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3)}\n.vb-best-label{font-size:9px;background:var(--gbg);color:var(--g);border:1px solid var(--gbr);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-weight:700}\n\n/* BACKTEST */\n.bt-sum{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(110px,1fr));gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px}\n.btm{background:var(--bg3);border-radius:var(--Rs);padding:10px;text-align:center}\n.btm .bv{font-size:21px;font-weight:700}\n.btm .bl{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx2);margin-top:2px}.btm .bs{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3)}\n.bt-wrap{overflow-x:auto}\n.bt-t{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:11px;min-width:780px}\n.bt-t th{padding:5px 6px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bdr2);font-size:9px;font-weight:600;color:var(--tx3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;white-space:nowrap}\n.bt-t td{padding:5px 6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bdr);white-space:nowrap}\n.bt-t tr:last-child td{border:none}\n.b{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px}\n.bH{background:var(--gbg);color:var(--g);border:1px solid var(--gbr)}\n.bM{background:var(--rbg);color:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--rbr)}\n.fi-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;margin-bottom:4px}\n.fi-lbl{width:120px;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2);text-align:right;flex-shrink:0}\n.fi-track{flex:1;height:17px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}\n.fi-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-left:6px;font-size:9px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}\n.disc{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);padding:8px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--bdr);margin-top:10px;line-height:1.6}\n.pc-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--R);padding:10px 12px;margin-bottom:7px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"app\">\n\n<div class=\"hdr\">\n  <div class=\"hdr-l\">\n    <div class=\"ico\">⚾</div>\n    <div>\n      <h1>MLB Betting Intelligence <span class=\"tag\" style=\"background:var(--pubg);color:var(--pu)\">v8</span></h1>\n      <p>Best EV per game · ML/RL coherence · Weather · H2H · Splits · BABIP regression · Auto pitcher blend · <strong style='color:var(--g)'>Apr 8, 2026</strong></p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px\">\n  <div class=\"hstats\" id=\"hstats\"></div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px\">\n    <span id=\"live-status\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2)\">Connecting...</span>\n    <span id=\"last-update\" style=\"font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3)\"></span>\n    <button onclick=\"fetchTodaySchedule()\" style=\"font-size:9px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--bdr2);background:var(--bg3);color:var(--b);cursor:pointer\">🔄 Refresh</button>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"tabs\">\n  <div class=\"tab active\" onclick=\"sw('pred',this)\">Predictions</div>\n  <div class=\"tab\" onclick=\"sw('value',this)\">Best Bets</div>\n  <div class=\"tab\" onclick=\"sw('back',this)\">Backtest</div>\n  <div class=\"tab\" onclick=\"sw('pitch',this)\">Pitchers</div>\n  <div class=\"tab\" onclick=\"sw('reg',this)\">Regression</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel active\" id=\"tab-pred\">\n  <div class=\"sec\" id=\"pred-date-label\">Sun Apr 5, 2026</div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px\">\n  <div id=\"slate-label\" style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--b)\">Wed Apr 8, 2026</div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px\">\n    <button onclick=\"switchSlate(-1)\" style=\"font-size:10px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--bdr2);background:var(--bg3);color:var(--tx2);cursor:pointer\">◀ Prev</button>\n    <button onclick=\"switchSlate(1)\" style=\"font-size:10px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--bdr2);background:var(--bg3);color:var(--tx2);cursor:pointer\">Next ▶</button>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"g5\" id=\"pred-metrics\"></div>\n  <div id=\"glist\"></div>\n  <div class='disc'>⚠ v8: Best bet = highest EV pick per game. ML/RL coherence: if RL value → model checks ML is also +EV on same side. Weather: outdoor parks have O/U adjusted for wind/temp. BABIP regression incorporated per pitcher. H2H 2025 and LHP/RHP splits included. For analysis only.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel\" id=\"tab-value\">\n  <div class=\"sec\">Best bet per game — today</div>\n  <div id=\"vblist\"></div>\n  <div class=\"disc\">One pick per game — highest EV. UNDER picks appear when model projected total is below market line after O/U calibration. Early 2026: pitching-heavy environment means more UNDERs expected. Weather/SP adjustments affect each total.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel\" id=\"tab-back\">\n  <div class=